### Denne automation tager et snapshot af tilstanden på min sonoshøjtaler og pauser musikken (hvis den spiller), når der tales i telefon ###
 
- id: '1599032944571'
  alias: 1. phonecall - sonos mute
  description: ''
  trigger:
  - entity_id: sensor.cs_mobil_phone_state
    platform: state
    to: offhook
  condition:
  - condition: zone
    entity_id: person.christian
    zone: zone.home
  action:
  - data: {}
    entity_id: media_player.kontoret
    service: sonos.snapshot
  - timeout: 00:00:01
    wait_template: ''
  - data: {}
    entity_id: media_player.kontoret
    service: media_player.media_pause
  mode: single
 
### Denne automation laver en "restore" af snapshottet, når opkaldet afsluttes. Så hvis der har været musik inden opkaldet, fortsættes hvor den pausede. Har der ikke været musik, forbliver højtaleren tavs. ###
- id: '1599033393434'
  alias: 3. phonecall end - resume sonos
  description: ''
  trigger:
  - entity_id: sensor.cs_mobil_phone_state
    from: offhook
    platform: state
  condition:
  - condition: zone
    entity_id: person.christian
    zone: zone.home
  action:
  - data: {}
    entity_id: media_player.kontoret
    service: sonos.restore
  mode: single
